title: Animated parody on Youtube

embed.description: Bloopers, wardrobe malfunctions and a few deaths feature in this animated League of Legends parody. Recommended for mature audiences. (15+) Credits: Drawn, animated and voiced by myself except Jinx's laugh which was voiced by MadamVicious and the long male scream by dinsfire, both from the freesound website listed below Background drawings are photoshopped images not drawn by me.

body: Hey I made this video with bad jokes and everything. Why not check it out. I can take criticism.
